com.adobe.fd.ccm.ccr.ccrDocumentInstance.api.model

Class CCRDocumentInstance

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.adobe.fd.ccm.ccr.ccrDocumentInstance.api.model.CCRDocumentInstance

  • public class CCRDocumentInstance
extends Object
    The CCRDocumentInstance class represents data and details of an Interactive Communication maintained as draft that can be saved and updated at storage-end before final submission.
